thread.title: groove pool grand opening 11pm gmt 17jun

comments.text: [groove pool] will have its opening lightshow 11pm gmt on 17jun17 all are welcome. dance classics will be played. for requests have them typed on a sheet.
thanks for every who came to see - jinx - delco - fazzi - emily - overviser and many others thank you.
your place was awesome and an excellent example of what's possible in vr and not reality. and that was extra fun  for me because it was on my 1 year vive anni-vr-sery. =)
